    <deprecated>false</deprecated>
    <description>Provides yearly information on the catalog price and Chapter 5 Life Limits
The &quot;Catalog List Prices&quot; table for each LLP (Life Limited Part) Part Number, linked to the LLP Template record, is organized by year. This table is intended for annual updates of part costs using information from the manufacturer. Once updated, the individual costs of LLPs can be utilized to calculate the total LLP cost for the entire engine stack, as well as to determine the annual OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturer) price escalation and a cost per cycle for the engine.
[MODULE: Asset]
[LOAD: Optional]
[PREREQUISITES: LLP Template]
[REPLACEMENT OBJECT API: NA]
[COMMENTS: NA]</description>
